VERSION HISTORY

v2.0.0 (2025-07-02): Major release with foundation model support
v1.5.0 (2024-12-15): Added transformer architectures and deployment tools
v1.0.0 (2024-06-01): Initial stable release with core functionality
v0.9.0 (2024-03-15): Beta release for community testing
v0.1.0 (2024-01-01): Alpha release with basic models

For detailed changelog, see: CHANGELOG.md

